We’ve improved the overall look and feel of the app with this update.
We’ve implemented more stylish versions of the homepage, the category pages, and overall app navigation, to better showcase our top offers, and to make it even easier for you to find what you’re looking for.
Any feedback or questions, please send them through to contact@topcashback.com.
